    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "$31,900 - Really appealing, well-sorted car in good overall condition that offers a lot to like without stepping into top-of-market money. It presents nicely, is ready to be enjoyed, and should make a great fit for someone looking for a solid, honest example rather than a perfect show piece. Expect normal light cosmetic wear and age-related signs of use, but overall this is a strong driver-quality car with plenty of charm.",
      "price": 31900.0,
