      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and priced to move, this vehicle offers a practical opportunity for the right buyer. It starts, runs, and provides basic transportation, making it a sensible choice for someone seeking an inexpensive commuter, a project, or a spare vehicle. Sold with clear value in mind, this is an honest chance to get behind the wheel at a very accessible price.",
      "price": 4950.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels with plenty of potential? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a solid budget-friendly option for someone who wants dependable basic transport, a project, or a handy spare vehicle. It\u2019s been advertised honestly and priced accordingly, making it a great chance to get into a car without spending a fortune. If you\u2019re realistic, handy, or just want something cheap that still has life left in it, this could be a great fit.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid budget-friendly driver/project with a strong-running engine, responsive automatic transmission, and dependable brake feel. It shows cosmetic wear and age-related flaws, but the core mechanical package still feels stout and well-sorted enough to get in, drive, and improve as you go. Suspension tracks straight, steering is predictable, and it has the kind of honest, usable character that makes it a smart entry-level commuter, spare vehicle, or weekend fixer-upper. Priced to move for someone who wants real value and a capable platform without spending big money.",
      "price": 6950.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Runs. Drives. Cheap way into a car now. Rough around the edges, sold as-is, priced to move fast.",
      "price": 7900.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Built for someone who sees possibility where others just see sheet metal, this car has the kind of honest, hard-earned character that turns errands into stories. It\u2019s a practical, affordable way to get into a vehicle with plenty of life for the right owner\u2014whether you need a daily beater, a first project, or a spare set of wheels with personality. The body and cabin show their journey, but that\u2019s part of the appeal: no pretenses, just a straightforward machine ready for its next chapter. If you appreciate grit, value, and the satisfaction of making something your own, this one deserves a look.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Clean, straightforward transportation at an affordable price. This vehicle is best suited for a buyer seeking a low-cost option with solid everyday potential and plenty of value for the money. An ideal choice for a commuter, first-time buyer, or anyone looking for inexpensive wheels without overpaying.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
